<p><b>After adding your 'oship' (case sensitive, no quotes) application. Then
return here by clicking on the <b>'oship' link in the top left</b> and
execute this <a href="http://localhost:8080/oship/setup">setup link.</a></b>
When your ADL files are finished processing; you will be redirected to the
Zope Management Interface (ZMI).<br>
Just click down through the menu on the top left to find the 'ar'. </p>

<p>The links below will provide you with a start into the world of
interoperable healthcare applications. </p>

