<p>OSHIP is open source software based on an open specification. Both the
specifications and the software are licensed under a business friendly
license allowing for both open source and proprietary applications to be
developed and still share semantically complete information. For more
information please join the OSHIP developer mailing list on <a
href="https://launchpad.net/oship/">Launchpad</a> by adding it to your
Launchpad profile and/or contact the lead developer <a
href="mailto:timothywayne.cook@gmail.com">Tim Cook</a>. </p>

